SPP will measure CME shocks where particle acceleration to high energies (protons to 10 GeV, electrons to a few tens of MeV) is thought to maximize (R<20RS\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
